<li><a href="/wiki/Malting_House_School" title="Malting House School">Malting House School</a>, a somewheat similar school that operated in the UK from 1924-1929.</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/The_Nova_Project" title="The Nova Project">The Nova Project</a>, Seattle, Washington is a public high school based on the same philosophy.</li>
